# Continuous Evaluation for retrieval-based LLMs pipelines

Continuous evaluation for retrieval-based LLMs pipelines.

## Installation

```bash
python3 -m pip install continuous_eval
```

## Getting Started

### Prerequisites

Tte code requires thr `OPENAI_API_KEY` and optionally an `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY`.

